==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: paperback
<hw>pa"per*back</hw> <pos>adj.</pos> <def>having a flexible binding; --
of books. Contrasted to <contr>hardcover</contr> or
<contr>hardbacked</contr> or <contr>hardbound</contr>.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> paperbacked, soft-bound, softcover,
softback.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

